            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "As mentioned, this is out of scope for `vim.lsp.buf` and it's already possible to implement this by programmatically moving the cursor.\n\nAlternatively, you could monkeypath `util.make_position_params` before calling `vim.lsp.buf.*`\n\n```lua\nlocal f = vim.lsp.util.make_position_params\nvim.lsp.util.make_position_params = ...\nvim.lsp.buf.references(...)\nvim.lsp.util.make_position_params = f\n```\n\nWe will this use case in mind for the future.",
